(63,	1,	'2026-04-24 01:30:19',	'2026-04-24 01:30:19',	'<h1>HELLO!</h1>					<h2>My name is Shamaiah Lee Cadut</h2>								<p data-interaction-id=\"e2f2ed7\"  >\n								A creative professional specializing in&nbsp;Graphic Design,&nbsp;Programming,&nbsp;AI Automation, and&nbsp;Social Media Marketing. I transform ideas into impactful digital experiences.\n					</p>\n					    	            <button data-interaction-id=\"7c94956\"  >\n            Get in touch\n        </button>\n    					    	            <button data-interaction-id=\"be5335c\"  >\n            Download Resume\n        </button>\n    															<img src=\"http://shamee.local/wp-content/plugins/elementor/assets/images/placeholder.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />																		\n		<img \n					data-interaction-id=\"f053eef\" \n									src=\"http://shamee.local/wp-content/plugins/elementor/assets/images/placeholder-v4.svg\"\n						/>\n								<h1 \n		data-interaction-id=\"298c5dc\" \n		class=\"e-298c5dc-c651d74 e-heading-base\" \n	>\n			About Me\n		</h1>\n		<p>Hello! I\'m Shamaiah Lee Cadut, a multifaceted creative professional with a passion for blending technology and design. My journey in the digital world has equipped me with a unique skill set that spans across graphic design, programming, AI automation, and social media marketing.<br /><br />I believe in the power of visual storytelling and innovative technology to create meaningful connections. Whether I\'m designing eye-catching graphics, developing intelligent automation solutions, crafting engaging social media campaigns, or writing code that brings ideas to life, my goal is always to deliver excellence.<br /><br />With hands-on experience in social media marketing and graphic design, I understand how to create content that not only looks amazing but also drives engagement and achieves business objectives. I\'m constantly learning and evolving with the latest trends in design, technology, and marketing to stay ahead of the curve.</